Violation of following guidelines leads to a deduction of points in exercise 3.

\begin{enumerate}
\item It is forbidden to use the deprecated functions
\texttt{gethostbyname}, \texttt{gethostbyaddr}, \texttt{gethostbyname2},
\texttt{gethostbyname\_r}, \texttt{gethostbyname2\_r}
or any other function of that family
documented on the man page \texttt{gethostbyname(3)}.
Use \texttt{getaddrinfo(3)} instead.
\end{enumerate}
